─── Inspiration / prior art ────────────────────────────────────────────────

This project's surface area (R3F + OSM Overpass → extruded buildings →
GLB export) was inspired by:

  cartesiancs/map3d (MIT, https://github.com/cartesiancs/map3d)
  Copyright (c) 2024 cartesiancs

@mnemopay/map3d is an independent implementation. No source code was
copied; the architecture pattern is the only thing shared, and that
pattern is itself common across OSM-3D projects (Overpass → footprint →
extrude → render). The cartesiancs/map3d README is acknowledged here
for community attribution, not for any license obligation.

